### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@projectId = PROJECT_ID_HERE
@clientId = CLIENT_ID_HERE

### 1. Crear un proyecto
POST {{baseUrl}}/project
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Reforma Casa Central",
  "projectCode": "REF-2024-001",
  "description": "Reforma integral de la casa central de la compañía",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "status": "activo",
  "budget": 50000,
  "startDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-06-30T00:00:00Z",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Principal",
    "number": "42",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### 2. Listar todos los proyectos
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Listar proyectos con filtro por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?name=Reforma&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Listar proyectos con filtro por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?client={{clientId}}&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5. Listar proyectos con filtro por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?status=activo&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 6. Listar proyectos activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?active=true&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 7. Listar proyectos ordenados por fecha de creación descendente
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?sort=-createdAt&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 8. Obtener un proyecto específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 9. Actualizar un proyecto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Reforma Casa Central - Fase 2",
  "status": "completado",
  "endDate": "2024-05-15T00:00:00Z"
}

### 10. Soft delete (archivar) un proyecto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=true
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 11. Hard delete (eliminar permanentemente) un proyecto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=false
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 12. Listar proyectos archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/archived?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 13. Restaurar un proyecto archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/restore
Authorization: {{authToken}}
